<p>Our most popular add-on allows users to purchase digital download files and have instant access to files securely after their purchase. Other features include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Sell&nbsp;the digital download files for an entire gallery for a single price</li>
<li>Allow users to download individual images in a gallery for free without needing to checkout, optionally set the maximum number of free downloads a user can have (based on IP).</li>
<li>Allow users to download the entire gallery for free without needing to checkout</li>
<li>Create downloadable products and choose the exact pixel sizes of the downloaded file. You can sell separate low and high-resolution files!</li>
<li>Optionally watermark the digital downloaded image, great when offering a free, low-resolution image download</li>
<li>Integrates with <a href="https://www.sunshinephotocart.com/docs/amazon-s3-integration/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WP Offload S3</a> (a free plugin) to allow you to have all your files stored in the cloud for unlimited file storage</li>
</ul>
